The paper discusses vulnerabilities and attacks on voice-controlled systems, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). It also discusses the need for a universal defense strategy, which could fall under the categories of software engineering (cs.SD) or systems and control (cs.SI). The paper also discusses the user interface aspect of voice-controlled systems, which could fall under human-computer interaction (cs.HC) or cybernetics (cs.CY).
